  "detailed_description": "Dwarves & Dungeons official version is finally here! There are currently three available characters, four maps with corresponding enemies and bosses. The game innovates based on match-3 gameplay, combining elements from rogue-like games to bring a unique and fresh experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/6ac7f62c032b2008860cc31b4ac5e427.avif?t=1724989937\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/282ae5bb14f8c1ac4fda6877908bc3b8.poster.avif?t=1724989937\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/282ae5bb14f8c1ac4fda6877908bc3b8.webm?t=1724989937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/282ae5bb14f8c1ac4fda6877908bc3b8.mp4?t=1724989937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In Dwarves & Dungeons, everything revolves around <strong>connecting lines</strong>, whether it's gathering strength to eliminate enemies, fortifying defense to stay away from danger, or picking up coins for future planning. Achieving these tasks all requires the connecting. Characters can gain experience points and level up after long-distance connections, learning beneficial skills along the way. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/135dd11e88ac53b9b8d9fb2254c68dd9.avif?t=1724989937\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/27ea4830a1952b15771d584d62e987e4.poster.avif?t=1724989937\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/27ea4830a1952b15771d584d62e987e4.webm?t=1724989937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/27ea4830a1952b15771d584d62e987e4.mp4?t=1724989937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The third character, the <strong>Warlock</strong>, is finally out! There are now three selectable characters, each with completely different mechanics, runes, and combat styles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/8b055bb974f0f1c3dbffb1578faa7d4f.avif?t=1724989937\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/5992c9a890dc693a03195896a130c5d6.poster.avif?t=1724989937\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/5992c9a890dc693a03195896a130c5d6.webm?t=1724989937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/5992c9a890dc693a03195896a130c5d6.mp4?t=1724989937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Get new runes during battles and make your own build to connect lines, eliminate enemies, and collect coins more efficiently.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/0febb46158705cba8fc68241d22bcc4c.avif?t=1724989937\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/0219f4afcf146af8ef54a8f77fe6c20e.poster.avif?t=1724989937\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/0219f4afcf146af8ef54a8f77fe6c20e.webm?t=1724989937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/0219f4afcf146af8ef54a8f77fe6c20e.mp4?t=1724989937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Various types of random events will occur on the game board. Some may enhance your Status, while others can update runes. But act quickly; once the time is up, they disappear.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/2be51faca99f8c3bdf5b08fa5f0b5b97.avif?t=1724989937\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/d0e2ca1d6edc5d0e1c382900ea3eddc9.poster.avif?t=1724989937\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/d0e2ca1d6edc5d0e1c382900ea3eddc9.webm?t=1724989937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1457690/extras/d0e2ca1d6edc5d0e1c382900ea3eddc9.mp4?t=1724989937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Whether victorious or not in battles, all collected coins can be used to construct the basement. Upgrade the blacksmith shop, craft scrolls in the workshop, strengthen basic Status in the cabin... Utilize the various facilities in the base to make adventures easier.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Tribute </h2><strong> This game was initially inspired by the famous game: Dungeon Raid. </strong>",
